events.name: 地下水路　監禁部屋へ移動
下水道　ストーリーイベント

parameters:
\n< Serena >What!? A swarm of slimes!? Are they trying to
kill us!?

\n< ？？？ >What's wrong? Are you scared of my little
slime friends and trying to run away?

\n< ？？？ >Then go home, you brat! This is my kingdom!
No one can capture me!

\n< Ghee >Hehehe...? Well then, what are you going to do?
Besides running away with your tail
between your legs, do you have anything
else you can do, huh?
\n< Serena >Yeah... I do feel like running away.
\n< Serena >...It took a lot of courage to come this far.

\n< Serena >But if we're being honest, all of this is
your fault.

\n< Serena >If I were to weigh anger and fear on a
scale, right now anger slightly
outweighs.

\n< Serena >That's why I can step forward. I can move
forward. If I don't give you a blow, I
won't be satisfied.
\n< Ghee >Hey brat, can't you see my slime-chan?

\n< Serena >I can see it. But I'll make it disappear
soon.

\n< Ghee >Hehehe...? Well then, what are you going to do?
Besides running away with your tail
between your legs, do you have anything
else you can do, huh?

\n< Serena >Makoto, the world is truly vast. Since coming
to this town, it has been a series of
surprises.

\n< Serena >I never thought there would be a human
who could communicate with slimes. No
wonder they can make the sewer their
hideout.
\n< Ghee >Hey brat, can't you see my slime-chan?

\n< Serena >I can see it, of course. But it will
disappear soon.
\n< Ghee >No, after all, you still can't see it!

\n< Serena >...So you were hiding something this huge.
But even though it was a surprise
attack, it was a failure.

\n< Ghee >Kukuu! Dammit! Even though you're laughing
your ass off, you're surprisingly agile,
aren't you?

\n< Ghee >Kukuu! Dammit! You're not just a brat after
all, you bastard!

\n< Serena >Criminal Ghee. I'm going to make you spill all
the details about the source of the
poison.

\n< Ghee >Shit... There's no way I'm getting caught, no
way...!
\n< Ghee >Slimes, protect me! Kill that brat!

\n< Ghee >I'm gonna melt you from the inside out,
turning your organs into mush like jam!
I'll dissolve you and devour you!

\n< Serena >Ngh... how could I be defeated by a mere
slime...!

\n< Ghee >Gyahaha! Take a good look, you little shit! This
is my power! The military might of my
kingdom!!!

\n< Ghee >Alright, good job! That's enough! Hand over that
brat to me!

\n< Ghee >With my adult cock, you know! Ghehehe!
Adults and children! Men and women!

\n< Ghee >I'll engrave the difference in our positions
into you thoroughly!! Oooohhh!!
\n< Serena >Ngh...! My, my ass...! Th-this person...!?

\n< Ghee >Hey!? Shit, listen to me! This low-
intelligence monster!
\n< Serena >C-Could it be that you can't control it...!?

\n< Serena >Nnku!?... Ahh!? It's entering... little by
little...!

\n< Serena >Ah, aaah... I-it's going... deeper...!
Deeper...! Inside...!?
\n< Serena >N-No... Ahh! This sensation... so intense...!

\n< Serena >Uuuh... Inside my body... It's... like this...
Ughh...!
\n< Serena >Ahh, no, no! It won't stop...!

\n< Serena >Wh-When... What is it...! You want... to do...!
Not kill...! Not devour...!

\n< Serena >It's disgusting, it's disgusting, it's
disgusting...!

\n< Serena >Are you searching for something...
touching... me... in that way...?!

\n< Ghee >I'm the king! The king's orders are
absolute, you know!

\n< Ghee >No, earlier I said to kill her! That was
just a slip of the tongue! Cancel that!
I'm the one who's going to enjoy it, you
know! Hey!
\n< Ghee >Don't mess around, you bastard...! Hey!
エネミー HK_黒スライム01-1
エネミー HK_黒スライム01-1

\n< Serena >......Hah... The slime escaped too. Should I say I
got lucky...?

\n< Serena >Or is it thanks to this man fainting? For
a moment, the slime's movement clearly
stopped...
\n< Serena >It started hurting when I remembered...

\n< Serena >The pain... it's coming from inside my
body... It's an unfamiliar pain. Even
though it was for a short time, I was
treated as they pleased...

\n< Serena >The sensation of being moved around inside
my stomach was incredibly disgusting...

\n< Serena >Just imagining what would have happened if I
had been completely engulfed is
terrifying...

\n< Serena >With this stamina... There's a big man in
front of me. In the end, I achieved my
goal, so it's fine...

\n< Serena >How to carry this person up. That's the
difficult part...

\n< Ghee >......Hehehe...... My slime-chan... my invincible
kingdom... aaaaah......!

\n< Ghee >Oh my, you're so strong even though you're
young! You're really strong! I-I'm
impressed!!
\n< Ghee >Uwehehe... That's the only thing I'm good at...

\n< Serena >*sigh* I used to think that adult men were
more respectable...

\n< Serena >Since coming to this town, my disappointment
has only grown. Or perhaps the people in
this town are just special?

\n< Serena >...Speaking of special. How exactly were you
controlling the slime?
\n< Serena >I've never heard of such a special skill.

\n< Ghee >Huh?... Ah, well... hehe, to control it like
that... I'm nothing special...

\n< Ghee >Ehehe... Then, just between us, sister, shall I
tell you my trade secret?

\n< Ghee >Inside this bottle... there's a little secret
packed in there.

\n< Ghee >If I have this, the slime won't attack
me... or rather, the owner... no, more
accurately, as long as I have this
bottle, it won't attack.

\n< Serena >Black liquid...? I wonder what it is? Some
kind of chemical?
\n< Ghee >Oh, really? It's just something like that.

\n< Serena >Sigh... But is this really such a
groundbreaking discovery? This town must
have struggled a lot with controlling
slimes too.

\n< Serena >With this liquid, I wonder how much those
struggles would be alleviated. No, there
are countless ways to utilize it...

\n< Serena >...If there was something like this, wouldn't
there have been no need to participate
in the distribution of poison?

\n< Serena >We could have made an enormous fortune no
matter how much.

\n< Ghee >Oh, well. This is just something I picked
up. It's not like I made it or anything.

\n< Ghee >Why would selling just this one bottle be
worth only a small amount of money?

\n< Ghee >Even if I were to use it for something, it's
beyond my capabilities...

\n< Serena >So, did you decide to use it to engage in
poison distribution by lurking in the
sewers?

\n< Serena >It's an unfathomable foolishness. A
discovery that could change the world...
packed into such a cheap bottle...

\n< Ghee >Oh no, that's not it. The fact that this
bottle is cheap is what's gross about
it, you know?

\n< Ghee >Doesn't this look unfinished and fragile just
by looking at it? That's why I'm doing
this.

\n< Ghee >I could use it to blindside and confuse
them by throwing it!
エネミー HK_黒スライム01-1
エネミー HK_黒スライム01-1

\n< Serena >I just thought it would be something like
that anyway.

\n< Serena >If you're prepared, it's no big deal to
throw a punch in the direction where you
hear the sound, even if you can't see
it.

\n< Serena >...However, the contents of the bottle that was
just thrown at me...

\n< Serena >So you're saying it escaped on its own,
meaning it was a slime? It had the power
to control other slimes...

\n< Serena >...Shouldn't we have not let it escape? But even if
we were to chase after it now...
